&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;ABOUT BIRGO&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Birgo Capital is a Pittsburgh-based private equity real estate firm with ~$340M in AUM. We acquire and operate multifamily properties with a team of 100+ people who believe that excellent operations and meaningful impact are not in conflict. We&#39;re on track to reach $1B in AUM by 2030.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Backed by 33 consecutive quarters of distributions and a national investor footprint, we are prepared to bring on our first Partner, Capital Formation.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;—&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;THE OPPORTUNITY&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;The Partner&lt;strong&gt; reports directly to the CEO &lt;/strong&gt;and is responsible for one outcome:&lt;strong&gt; raising $50M–$100M&lt;/strong&gt; of accredited investor equity annually.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is an end-to-end ownership role. From sourcing and relationship development through closed capital and reinvestment, you&#39;ll build the engine and own the results. Our leadership is available and will engage at key moments, but the pipeline, the process, and the performance are yours.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;—&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;WHAT YOU&#39;LL DO&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build, manage, and expand a capital raising engine from your own network and relationships&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Independently source capital through HNWIs, family offices, and accredited investor referral networks&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide feedback on offering structure, investor objections, and messaging to sharpen conversion&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Steward full authority for the lifecycle of your talent. You are responsible for the &quot;Who&quot; aspect of your high-performance capital formation unit.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Drive conversion from first conversation through closed commitment and reinvestment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Engage as a trusted peer and advisor (not a salesperson)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain a forward-looking pipeline in HubSpot with forecasting rigor&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with IR, Legal, Marketing, and the CEO on Reg D offering execution&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;—&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;WHO THRIVES HERE&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You are self-starting and goal-driven. You do not need a playbook.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You are competitive and achievement-oriented. You track your own numbers because you want to win.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You make quick decisions under pressure.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You are a persuasive communicator who earns trust through credibility and integrity.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You are entrepreneurial. You think and act like an owner.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;—&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;WHAT WE&#39;RE LOOKING FOR&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
